&quot;STARSLIP&quot; Web Comic

&quot;Starslip&quot; (starslip.chainsawsuit.com) by Kris Straub is a hybrid science fiction / fine art comic, set in the distant future on the Terran Directorate Ship Fuseli, a &quot;luxury battle cruiser&quot; converted into a museum ship.  The strip began as a send-up of artistic and science fiction tropes, but gradually incorporated longer and more complicated storylines.  Its main characters include Memnon Vanderbeam, the fussy, arrogant curator of the Fuseli, Cutter Edgewise, the drunk ex-pirate who is now the Fuseli's pilot, and Mr. Jinx, a cirbozoid, a stoic insectoid alien.  The strip was originally named &quot;Starshift Crisis&quot; until a potential copyright issue with the video game &quot;StarShift: The Zaran Legacy&quot; caused Straub to change it to &quot;Starslip Crisis.&quot;  Later, the name was shortened to simply &quot;Starslip.&quot;

This torrent collects the entire run of &quot;Starslip&quot; comics from 2005 through 2012.  The strips are collected into CBR files by year, though with some &quot;fudging&quot; to prevent story chapters from splitting between volumes
